%p Care of the talented <span class="vcard"><a class="url fn" href="http://twitter.com/msharp" rel="met colleague friend">Mr Sharp</a></span>, I discovered what I'm certain is the most beautiful design object I've ever seen and it has me thinking.

%p The object is an artistic filmic piece on architecture. It&rsquo;s gorgeously shot, lovingly detailed, fantastically composed, and... <strong>entirely computer generated</strong>.

%h2 The Third & The Seventh
